==English==
===Idiom===
'''[[been]] [[there]], [[done]] [[that]], [[bought]] the [[T-shirt]]'''

#''(jocular)'' Expresses the speaker's complete [[familiarity]] with a situation (as though with a tourist destination), with overtones of [[cynicism]] or [[exhaustion]].  Abbreviation (in Internet usage): '''[[BTDTBTTS]]'''

